A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Article 4 of Chapter 3 of Title 8 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
2 relating to fair housing, so as to provide for artificial intelligence or automated decision tools
3 in actions for discriminatory housing practices; to prohibit the use of certain defenses in
4 actions for discriminatory housing practices; to prohibit the use of artificial intelligence or
5 automated decision tools without human oversight in making certain housing determinations;
6 to prohibit making certain housing determinations using artificial intelligence or automated
7 decision tools without certain disclosures; to provide for enforcement by Attorney General;
8 to provide for fines; to provide for a short title; to provide for definitions; to provide for
9 related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
11 SECTION 1.
12 This Act shall be known and may be cited as the "Fair and Future Ready Housing Act."
13 SECTION 2.
14 Article 4 of Chapter 3 of Title 8 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to fair
15 housing, is amended by adding a new Code section to read as follows:
